## Wallet Architecture (Critical — Never Change)

```
User personal wallet (MetaMask/RainbowKit):
  → Identity + auth ONLY
  → NEVER touched by agents
  → User's own keys always safe

User agent wallet (DCW):
  → Created by AgentFlow on premium signup
  → Agents execute ALL transactions FROM here
  → User deposits USDC manually
  → Spending limits enforced before every DCW call
  → Stored in Supabase wallets table (never in files)

AgentFlow treasury wallet (DCW):
  → Receives subscription payments
  → One wallet, created in bootstrap

Per agent: two DCW wallets
  → owner_wallet: ERC-8004 identity registration
  → validator_wallet: record reputation for other agents
```

