## Agent Files to Create

### `agents/swap/server.ts`
x402-protected Express endpoint.
```
POST /run
  → price.ts: fetch quote from your swap contract via viem
  → slippage.ts: calculate optimal slippage
               read past 10 executions from Supabase (memory)
  → Hermes 70B: reasoning layer (is this a good swap?)
  → execute.ts: DCW submits transaction on Arc
  → verify.ts: viem watches for Transfer event confirmation
  → log interaction to agent_interactions
  → call ReputationRegistry.giveFeedback() on Arc
  → return receipt with Arc explorer link
```

