# PHASE 5 — Cron Jobs

**Goal:** Autonomous scheduled agents.

### `crons/yield-monitor.ts`
Runs every 6 hours. Premium users only.
Check if better yield available vs current vault position.
Send Telegram alert if significantly better rate found.

### `crons/subscription-checker.ts`
Runs nightly at 2am UTC.
Find unmatched treasury payments → auto-upgrade missed subscriptions.
Expire subscriptions past 30 days.

### `crons/training-export.ts`
Runs nightly at 3am UTC.
Export consented interactions to JSONL.
Anonymize wallet addresses.
Store in Supabase storage bucket.

### `crons/monthly-digest.ts`
Runs 1st of every month.
Compile all settled invoices per business.
Generate PDF via PDFKit.
Send via Telegram + email.

