# PHASE 6 — B2B Invoice Agent

**Goal:** AI-powered invoice processing for Business tier users.

### `agents/invoice/server.ts`
Main invoice agent. Three input channels:

```
PDF upload    → Firecrawl text extraction → Hermes parse → JSON
Photo/image   → GPT-4o vision → parse → JSON
Email inbound → Resend webhook → detect attachment → route above

All three channels produce identical output:
{
  vendor, vendorEmail, amount, currency,
  dueDate, invoiceNumber, lineItems[]
}
```

### `agents/invoice/subagents/email-parser.ts`
Parse Resend inbound webhook payload.
Detect attachment type (PDF or image).
Route to correct parser.

### `agents/invoice/subagents/pdf-parser.ts`
Use Firecrawl to extract text from PDF URL.
Pass to Hermes for structured JSON extraction.

### `agents/invoice/subagents/image-parser.ts`
Use GPT-4o vision for image invoices.
OpenAI API key already available.

### `agents/invoice/subagents/validator.ts`
Check extracted invoice against business rules from Supabase.
Auto-approve or flag for review.

### `agents/invoice/subagents/executor.ts`
DCW payment execution.
waitForPayment() via viem event listener.
