# Start Here — First File to Write

**`scripts/bootstrap.ts`**

This runs ONCE before first deploy. It:
1. Creates the Circle WalletSet
2. Creates the treasury wallet
3. Creates owner + validator wallet pairs for all 8 agents
4. Registers ERC-8004 identity for each agent on Arc Testnet
5. Stores everything in Supabase wallets table
6. Outputs what to add to Railway env vars manually

After bootstrap runs successfully, add to Railway:
- WALLET_SET_ID
- TREASURY_WALLET_ADDRESS

Then never run bootstrap again.
